聖希爾達學院的學生出現在[[第四台_(英國)|第四台]]的紀錄片《[[學院女孩|學院女孩]]》中，該紀錄片在2002年播出。<ref>Anthea Milnes [http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/2002/sep/05/gender.uk1 "No men please, we're studying",] {{Wayback|url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/2002/sep/05/gender.uk1 |date=20100930224948 }} ''The Guardian'', 5 September 2002</ref>

